metadata.name: Medusozoa No. 1 (white)
metadata.description:
Medusozoa No. 1 (white) 
Digital Painting
300 x 300 dpi
2022

Medusozoa Cnidaria have been in existence for at least 500 million years, making them the oldest multi-organ animal group. Fascinated by their physiology, form and behavior, I find them to be an ideal subject to visually meditate upon.
